Build a modern, production-ready AI-powered Project Management web application using Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, Framer Motion, Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL, NextAuth/Auth.js, and OpenAI API.

The application should have a premium UI inspired by Linear, Notion, and Jira with smooth animations, glassmorphism, dark/light mode, responsive layouts, and excellent UX.

====================================
PROJECT NAME
====================================

ProjectFlow AI

